using AzureNextGen = Pulumi.AzureNextGen;

    public MyStack()
    {
        var capacityDetails = new AzureNextGen.PowerBIDedicated.Latest.CapacityDetails("capacityDetails", new AzureNextGen.PowerBIDedicated.Latest.CapacityDetailsArgs

            },

            },
        });

}

			},
		})

			return err
		}
		return nil
	})
